<plot>Two boys are swimming in a small lake where a 'No Bathing Allowed' sign is prominently posted. Soon they are joined in the water by several more boys. But a policeman spots them, and orders them all to come out. The boys obey him, and come up on the shore, but then they have a surprise for the policeman.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?621364</url></doc>
